
.. title:: Plugins

Job Generator Plugins for the IDL Job Parallel Framework
========================================================
Job generator plugins can be loaded for use with the IDL Job Parallel Framework
to output job files supporting different parallel platforms.

Users
-----
Users can load a plugin into the Framework by passing it's plugin ident to the
`load_generator_plugin` proceedure. See individual plugin description for
details and plugin ident.

Developers
----------
Developers wishing to support a particular parallel (or serial) platform
through the Framework can write their own plugins as described in the
`Writing Plugins` documentation.

